data.title: What is L5 'precision dual‑frequency GPS', why is Apple using it, and do you need it?
data.meta_description: Apple is packing 'precision dual‑frequency GPS' into the iPhone 14 Pro and the Apple Watch Ultra. But what is it, and what benefits will it bring?
